description: Crypt-Oink is Japan’s first blockchain game on the Ethereum network featuring crypto collectibles called Cryptons that can be bred, collected and traded. Over 3 trillion of these pig-like creatures exist with various colours and patterns. Cryptons can also trained to augment parameters affecting their strength in “Gran Ton Rismo”, Crypt-Oink’s 3D racing game.
name: Crypt-Oink
